"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?13/6/13416?source=see_link\">",
"      Management of malignant pleural effusions",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?31/16/32008?source=see_link\">",
"      Hospice: Philosophy of care and appropriate utilization in the United States",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <br/>",
"     The following organizations also provide reliable health information.",
"    </p>",
